<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>客製化靜觀瓶面板</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="lang-switch">
        <button id="btnZh" class="lang-btn active">中文</button>
        <button id="btnEn" class="lang-btn">EN</button>
      </div>
      <h1 id="title">客製化靜觀瓶面板</h1>
      <p id="subtitle">選擇心情、顏色、形狀、音樂與圖像，立即生成你的靜觀瓶預覽。</p>
    </header>

    <main class="grid">
      <section class="panel card">
        <h2 id="controlsTitle">控制面板</h2>

        <label for="mood" id="labelMood">心情</label>
        <select id="mood">
          <option value="anxious">焦慮 / Anxiety</option>
          <option value="angry">憤怒 / Angry</option>
          <option value="tired">疲倦 / Tired</option>
          <option value="happy">開心 / Happy</option>
          <option value="calm" selected>平靜 / Calm</option>
        </select>

        <label for="color" id="labelColor">顏色</label>
        <select id="color">
          <option value="auto" selected>自動推薦 / Auto</option>
          <option value="blue">藍色 / Blue</option>
          <option value="green">綠色 / Green</option>
          <option value="pink">粉紅 / Pink</option>
          <option value="purple">紫色 / Purple</option>
          <option value="teal">藍綠 / Teal</option>
          <option value="rainbow">彩虹色 / Rainbow</option>
        </select>

        <label for="shape" id="labelShape">形狀</label>
        <select id="shape">
          <option value="round" selected>圓瓶 / Round</option>
          <option value="tall">細長瓶 / Tall</option>
          <option value="square">方瓶 / Square</option>
          <option value="heart">心形瓶 / Heart</option>
          <option value="tube">試管瓶 / Tube</option>
        </select>

        <label for="density" id="labelDensity">閃粉密度</label>
        <select id="density">
          <option value="low">少量 / Low</option>
          <option value="mid" selected>中等 / Medium</option>
          <option value="high">較多 / High</option>
        </select>

        <label for="imgUpload" id="labelImage">上傳圖像</label>
        <input id="imgUpload" type="file" accept="image/*" />

        <label for="audioUpload" id="labelAudio">上傳音樂</label>
        <input id="audioUpload" type="file" accept="audio/*" />

        <label class="toggle">
          <input type="checkbox" id="musicToggle" checked />
          <span id="labelMusic">背景音樂 / Background music</span>
        </label>

        <div class="btn-row">
          <button id="btnRender">生成預覽 / Generate Preview</button>
          <button id="btnAnim">開始動畫 / Start Animation</button>
        </div>

        <div id="info" class="output"></div>
        <p class="small" id="note">可作為開放日展示，也可再擴充成 PNG 或 GIF 匯出。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="card preview-card">
        <canvas id="canvas" width="900" height="900"></canvas>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <audio id="bgm" loop preload="auto"></audio>
  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
